<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>" ساقط<span class="c1">". "</span>الكشاف" <span class="c2">(٤/ ٢٦٢)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
